nText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hsx1665702626834.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsx1665702626834.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsx1665702626834.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hsx1665702626834\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n /ilv\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hsx1665702626834___ilv_485895\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149594e1_d149595e1_d149596e1\">Compile the specified components using the indicated severity level for the compiler message <code class=\"ph codeph\">1000 - #Include <var class=\"keyword varname\">IncludeScript</var> not found</code>.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__topic_d149597e1_d149598e1_d149599e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149600e1_d149601e1_d149602e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ilv</span> = <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>| <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__topic_d107752e1_d107753e1_d107754e1_d107755e1_d107756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623536e90\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149606e1_d149607e1_d149608e1\">This <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ilv</span> switch can be used on its own, or as a sub-switch with the following:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d51986e1_d51987e1_d51988e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sww1665702625667.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sww1665702625667.html\" title=\"Compile all types of compilable main development objects, including components, modeled entities, and global objects.\">/all</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d51989e1_d51990e1_d51991e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yqf1665702625882.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqf1665702625882.html\" title=\"Compile application shells.\">/aps or /app</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d51992e1_d51993e1_d51994e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtz1665702626248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtz1665702626248.html\" title=\"Compile dynamic server pages.\">/dsp</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d51995e1_d51996e1_d51997e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ars1665702626915.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ars1665702626915.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface entity service components.\">/esv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d51998e1_d51999e1_d52000e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvm1665702627074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvm1665702627074.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface form components.\">/frm</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52004e1_d52005e1_d52006e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kjb1665702652886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kjb1665702652886.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface report components.\">/rpt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52007e1_d52008e1_d52009e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"umc1665702653094.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umc1665702653094.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface session service components.\">/ssv</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52010e1_d52011e1_d52012e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gku1665702653234.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gku1665702653234.html\" title=\"Compile Uniface service components.\">/svc</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52013e1_d52014e1_d52015e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prm1665702626469.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prm1665702626469.html\" title=\"Compile static server pages.\">/usp</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__topic_d107757e1_d107758e1_d107759e1_d107760e1_d107761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623536e196\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52016e1_d52017e1_d52018e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>—set the severity to <code class=\"ph codeph\">info</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52019e1_d52020e1_d52021e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>—set the severity to <code class=\"ph codeph\">warning</code> (default)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52022e1_d52023e1_d52024e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>—set the severity to <code class=\"ph codeph\">error</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__li_d52025e1_d52026e1_d52027e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var>—name of the component to compile; wildcards are allowed. If omitted, all objects are compiled.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__topic_d107762e1_d107763e1_d107764e1_d107765e1_d107766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623536e239\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__d6270e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__topic_d107767e1_d107768e1_d107769e1_d107770e1_d107771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623536e251\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149621e1_d149622e1_d149623e1\">By default, if Uniface cannot find a specified IncludeScript during compilation, it issues a warning message: (<code class=\"ph codeph\">1000 - (Preprocessor) #INCLUDE <var class=\"keyword varname\">IncludeName</var> Not Found</code>).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149624e1_d149625e1_d149626e1\">Since missing IncludeScripts can cause unexpected behavior, it can be useful to set the severity to <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code> (error), which prevents the component from being compiled.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__p_d149627e1_d149628e1_d149629e1\">This switch has the same effect as the assignment setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$INCLUDE_NOT_FOUND_LEVEL</span>. If both are specified, the command line switch takes precedence over the assignment setting.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsx1665702626834__section_dcy_3mh_ccc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d623536e278\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ilv</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">For example, the following command compiles all components starting with\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">SA</code> and sets the severity level for <code class=\"ph codeph\">#Include not\n               found</code> messages to <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code> (error):</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">/dsp /ilv=2 sa*</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cxn1665702653378.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$INCLUDE_NOT_FOUND_LEVEL</a><p>Set the message severity for the compiler message #Include not found.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528358\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528358\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/ilv Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /ilv Compile the specified components using the indicated severity level for the compiler message 1000 - #Include IncludeScript not found . /ilv = = { 0 | 1 | 2 } { Profile } Used With This /ilv switch can be used on its own, or as a sub-switch with the following: /all /aps or /app /dsp /esv /frm /rpt /ssv /svc /usp Parameters 0 —set the severity to info 1 —set the severity to warning (default) 2 —set the severity to error Profile —name of the component to compile; wildcards are allowed. If omitted, all objects are compiled. Use With ide —Uniface IDE Description By default, if Uniface cannot find a specified IncludeScript during compilation, it issues a warning message: ( 1000 - (Preprocessor) #INCLUDE IncludeName Not Found ). Since missing IncludeScripts can cause unexpected behavior, it can be useful to set the severity to 2 (error), which prevents the component from being compiled. This switch has the same effect as the assignment setting $INCLUDE_NOT_FOUND_LEVEL . If both are specified, the command line switch takes precedence over the assignment setting. Example: Using /ilv For example, the following command compiles all components starting with SA and sets the severity level for #Include not found messages to 2 (error): /dsp /ilv=2 sa* Related Links $INCLUDE_NOT_FOUND_LEVEL Set the message severity for the compiler message #Include not found. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}